## Notes:
- Materials include gravel, crushed stone, asphalt, cement, steel  
- Labour includes Survey, Earthworks, Pavement, Bridge, QA/QC, Environmental, Admin  
- Equipment includes Excavators, Graders, Rollers, Trucks  
- Contingency covers weather delays, price increases, minor errors  
